import React from 'react'
  import { MDXTag } from '@mdx-js/tag'
  import { Playground, PropsTable } from 'docz'
import { Grid, Box  } from '../../lib'

export default ({components, ...props}) => <MDXTag name="wrapper"  components={components}>
<MDXTag name="h1" components={components} props={{"id":"grid"}}>{`Grid`}</MDXTag>
<Playground __position={0} __codesandbox={`undefined`} __code={`<Grid min="300px" gap="20px">
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
  <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
</Grid>`} __scope={{props,Grid,Box}}>
  <Grid min="300px" gap="20px">
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
    <Box background="#CCC" height="100px" />
  </Grid>
</Playground>
<PropsTable of={Grid} /></MDXTag>
